#Title Chords example

@1 piano

ABC @1

;; Major triad
A o4  c  d  e   f  g   a  b  r
B o4  e  f+ g+  a  b  >c+ d+ r
C o4  g  a  b  >c  d   e  f+ r

;; Minor triad
A o4  c  d  e   f  g   a  b  r
B o4  e- f  g   a- b- >c  d  r
C o4  g  a  b  >c  d   e  f+ r

;; Augmented triad
A o4  c  d   e  f  g   a  b  r
B o4  e  f+  g+ a  b  >c+ d+ r
C o4  g+ a+ >c  c+ d+  f  g  r

